      <guid>/wily/dec-2023/20231218/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Setting up a systemd service for openvpn
Create a systemd service file in the path &lt;code&gt;/lib/systemd/system/openvpn-vinay.service&lt;/code&gt; with the following contents where &lt;code&gt;vinay.ovpn&lt;/code&gt; is the openvpn cert file within the location.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;code-block relative mt-6 first:mt-0 group/code&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Description=To access deeproot office infrastructure
After=multi-user.target

[Service]
ExecStart=sudo openvpn /etc/openvpn/vinay.ovpn

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;opacity-0 transition group-hover/code:opacity-100 flex gap-1 absolute m-[11px] right-0 top-0&#34;&gt;
