      <description>
        
        
        &lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Signing statements using GPG key&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Put the statement in a document or textfile like file.txt &lt;code&gt;gpg --clearsign file.txt&lt;/code&gt;
A file called file.txt.asc will be created which is gpg signed statement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Installing iosevka font&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://phd-sid.ethz.ch/debian/fonts-iosevka/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;https://phd-sid.ethz.ch/debian/fonts-iosevka/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Controlling audio within the terminal&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;pactl set-sink-volume 0 +10%&lt;/code&gt; : to increase the volume by 10%&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;pactl set-sink-volume 0 -10%&lt;/code&gt; : to decrease the volume by 10%&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

